data.description: Wonderful ranch-style brick home has plenty of space, functionality, updates, and makes for an amazing price point into Libertyville. Upon entry, you are greeted with a newly remodeled modern-style fireplace that is the center piece for the great room with beautiful large windows. Leading to the kitchen boasting white quartz countertops, 42" white cabinets, double sink with disposal, double oven, and an eat-in space. Large addition was built by a past owner to provide a very versatile space - currently used as formal dining, however could be a second living space, office, play room, etc. Both living spaces are spacious and have an abundance of natural light. All 3 beds on the main level, and bathroom has been completely remodeled to 2022 standards. Home has been very well taken care of, inside and out, siding and roof were done within the past 6 years, and the entire home interior was professionally painted within the last 2 years. Tons of potential to create more finished square footage in the unfinished basement - add additional bed(s) and bath, living space, bar, and more. Driveway and Additional Parking in Back of Home, allowing for easy 3 point turns, basketball court, and/or patio furniture, plus plenty of grass space as well This home is a gem, come see ASAP!
